{"tid":2418380,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"港超聯　愉園天水圍飛馬欠交保險金遭暫時禁賽","createTime":"2021-02-22T14:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T15:32:39.000Z","uid":363990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"73953ad6a94ef827597f2c3eb80a5e4a817a0366","tid":2418380,"uid":363990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T14:28:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20210222/bkn-20210222220213580-0222_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20210222%2Fbkn-20210222220213580-0222_00882_001.html&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XoTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=c74dcb14\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20210222/bkn-20210222220213580-0222_00882_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n香港足球總會周一（22日）宣布，由於天水圍飛馬、愉園未有如期繳付有關「綜合保險保障協議」費用，被罰禁止參與今季港超所有賽事直至繳清相關費用。至於原定於今周三（24日）出戰「菁英盃」4強的愉園，無論如何都未能趕及上訴或繳清欠款，換言之被取消參賽資格，對手理文自動進身決賽。<br />\n<br />\n香港joke球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b562be4d718494fb1bb44fb8a27233bc4b11e9","tid":2418380,"uid":290870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T14:36:52.000Z","msg":"老細自己都無錢，點玩？"},{"pid":"71488dac4115c94b39c3643b6d99c626617cf817","tid":2418380,"uid":169208,"like":6,"dislike":12,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T14:47:48.000Z","msg":"球員業餘 球隊業餘 管理層業餘<br />\n仲屌人唔入場睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c79b5d6f05ddd1f49775e5b36c56096aca92e4","tid":2418380,"uid":6689,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"71488dac4115c94b39c3643b6d99c626617cf817","tid":2418380,"uid":169208,"like":6,"dislike":12,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T14:47:48.000Z","msg":"球員業餘 球隊業餘 管理層業餘<br />\n仲屌人唔入場睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T14:55:49.000Z","msg":"係屌人唔入場睇仲要覺得好威咁屌香港足球啫"},{"pid"